Package: stegcore
Version: 4.0.2-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Daniel Iwugo <daniel@themalwarefiles.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/The-Malware-Files/Stegcore
Depends: libc6, libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0, libgtk-3-0t64 | libgtk-3-0, libsoup-3.0-0, libjavascriptcoregtk-4.1-0
Description: Crypto-steganography toolkit (CLI and desktop GUI)
 Stegcore combines encryption and steganography. It encrypts your
 payload and hides the ciphertext inside ordinary image or audio files.
 Features three AEAD ciphers (Ascon-128, ChaCha20-Poly1305, AES-256-GCM),
 deniable dual-payload mode, built-in steganalysis suite with five
 detectors, and both GUI and CLI interfaces.
 .
 This package installs the "stegcore" command-line tool and the
 "stegcore-gui" desktop application, with a launcher entry and icon.
 .
 Intended for journalists, activists, security researchers, and CTF players.
